node.text: Aside from the Danger Ranger 9000 Saturday night I get to look forward to drifting with @vaughngittinjr and @chelseadenofa on Friday night!!! Plus we’re doing a small competition for the drivers. There’s still driver slots open and plenty of tickets available to come watch in person! Tickets are available at TheFoat.com and we will have them for sale at the gate!!! #RTR

node.text:
Watch the vid (it's only 2 mins) and hopefully you guys can understand where i'm at. Sorry to anyone who this inconveniences... believe me, this sucks for us too. 

Due to continued uncertainty, the August 15th Indy Cleetus and Cars, and August 29th Bradenton Cleetus and Cars have been postponed to 2021. For everyone who has purchased an advance ticket for the Bradenton event, you will receive a refund from The Foat (the ticketing service). 

For those that have purchased tickets to Cleetus and Cars INDY in advance, your tickets will be good for:
1)The rescheduled event. 
2)The Lucas Oil Raceway- August 22nd Night Before 500 event
3)If you require a refund, please follow the directions below.
***PLEASE RESPOND by August 10th with decision on use of you tickets***

Tickets (General Admission, Parking, Racer Participants, and Camping) will be valid for the rescheduled date. 

To use your tickets for the August 22nd Night before 500, please contact Lucas Oil Raceway at mailto:lucasoilraceway@nhra.com with your name and account number, we will then have your tickets transferred.
 
Refund process: Customers may contact Lucas Oil Raceway at mailto:lucasoilraceway@nhra.com with your Name and account number for a refund.  Refunds may take up to 5-7 business days to appear on your account.

-Cleet
